The Python code above get the CPS DATA 2020 that we need from CENSUS.
The variables are explained in a separate file in this directory.
The CSV file for data is also in this directory with name cps2020_v1.CSV.
In the Codes and results we use this data, for the methodology and other numerical explanation, please look at the readme file at the related directory.

